UID:zgao367iKFkmLX2Ot6zwl
SUMMARY:Vital Sculpt HIIT Class with Seattle Jazzercise
DTSTAMP:20260314T160735Z
DTSTART:20260317T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Phinney Center\\\, Blue Building\\\, Room 7: This invigorating 
	HIIT-style exercise class promotes strength\\\, vitality\\\, and long-term
	 hormone health with a science-backed blend of targeted sculpting\\\, high
